 Capo2G drops his latest track along with a video ‘HAAIA‘ This track has a street theme filled with energy and colour. The “HAAIA” (Hottest African Artist In America) video features American celebrities RazB (B2K), Big Percy, comedian Red Grant among others. “HAAIA” was shot in Las Vegas by TGOBAY. Listen to the track below: https://www.bellanaija.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/Capo2G-HAAIA.mp3 Download Watch the video below The post New Music + Video: Capo2G — HAAIA (Hottest African Artist In America) appeared first on BellaNaija – Showcasing Africa to the world. Read today!. Source: Bella Naija